thread.title: French unemployment falls to lowest since 2009

title: French unemployment falls to lowest since 2009
text:
French unemployment falls to lowest since 2009 6:41pm IST - 01:39 
France's unemployment rate fell below 9 percent for the first time since 2009, registering a sharp drop that is likely to boost President Emmanuel Macron's efforts to reform the country's economy. David Pollard reports.
